fabric.extension

Interface FabricExt

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassBodyExt_c, LocatedExt_c, NewExt_c, NewFabricArrayExt_c, NewLabelExt_c, NodeExt_c, PrincipalExprExt_c

    public interface FabricExt
    This interface tags all fabric extension objects. All FabricExt objects should be the second extension of an ast node, i.e. if n is a node, then n.ext.ext refers to the FabricExt object ( n.ext should be a JifExt).
    Author:
    mdgeorge
